# PromptPal Environment Variables

## Required for Development

# Convex Backend URL
# Get this from your Convex dashboard (Settings > Deployment)
EXPO_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL=https://your-team-your-project.convex.cloud

# Convex Site URL (for actions)
# Usually same as EXPO_PUBLIC_CONVEX_URL
EXPO_PUBLIC_CONVEX_SITE_URL=https://your-team-your-project.convex.site

# Clerk Authentication
# Get this from Clerk dashboard (API Keys > Publishable Key)
EXPO_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...

# Clerk JWT Issuer Domain
# Get this from Clerk dashboard (Configure > JWT Templates)
# Format: https://your-domain.clerk.accounts.dev
CLERK_JWT_ISSUER_DOMAIN=https://your-domain.clerk.accounts.dev

# Auto-generated by Convex CLI (npx convex dev)
# Format: team:project or prod:project
CONVEX_DEPLOYMENT=

## Optional

# RevenueCat client (Expo / iOS)
# EXPO_PUBLIC_REVENUECAT_IOS_API_KEY=appl_...
# EXPO_PUBLIC_REVENUECAT_ENTITLEMENT_KEY=PromptPal Pro
# EXPO_PUBLIC_REQUIRE_SUBSCRIPTION=0   # set to 1 to block app access until Pro is active on iOS
#
# Paywall legal links
# EXPO_PUBLIC_PRIVACY_POLICY_URL=https://your-domain.example/privacy
# EXPO_PUBLIC_TERMS_OF_USE_URL=https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/
#
# Convex server env (set these in Convex, not Expo):
# REVENUECAT_API_KEY=appl_...            # RevenueCat REST API key
# REVENUECAT_ENTITLEMENT_KEY=PromptPal Pro
# REQUIRE_PRO_FOR_AI=0                  # set to 1 to require Pro for Convex AI actions
#
# Pair EXPO_PUBLIC_REQUIRE_SUBSCRIPTION=1 with REQUIRE_PRO_FOR_AI=1
# when the product should block both navigation and AI usage until Pro is active.
# If only the client flag is on, the UI is gated but direct AI calls can still work.
# If only the Convex flag is on, onboarding and app navigation stay open but AI actions
# can return SUBSCRIPTION_REQUIRED.
# When both flags are on, paywall resolution happens before onboarding.

# Note: EXPO_PUBLIC_GEMINI_API_KEY is NOT needed
# AI operations now go through Convex backend

## Migration Notes

# OLD environment variables (no longer used):
# - EXPO_PUBLIC_AI_PROXY_URL    (removed)
# - EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL           (removed)
#
# See docs/operations/CONVEX_MIGRATION.md for full migration guide
